<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span></font><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge and expressing an interest in our IR35 Protect policy. I've attached some information regarding the policies we offer.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Our </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Legal Expenses</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> product provides up to £100,000 of legal cover for IR35 status enquiries, jury service cover, debt recovery and much more.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Additionally, you can get up to £100,000 of cover for any taxes, interest and penalties in relation to an IR35 enquiry with Kingsbridge’s </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">IR35 Protect </b><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">packages. It’s also designed to flex to indemnify whoever is held liable by HMRC, giving both you and your fee payer peace of mind. You can also benefit from unlimited IR35 Status reviews with our Premium IR35 Protect policy.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Call </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808 740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> to start your cover today.<br></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808740</span></p>]]></td>
